---
// Values Section - Core Principles
---

<section class="pb-36 container-fluid">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
    
    <div class="mb-12">
      <h3 class="font-display font-bold text-2xl text-white mb-2">Core Operating Principles</h3>
      <p class="text-zinc-400">The code that governs the architecture.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
      <!-- Value 1 -->
      <div class="p-6 rounded-2xl bg-panel border soft-border hover:border-orange-500/30 transition-colors group">
        <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-orange-500/10 flex items-center justify-center text-orange-500 mb-4 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
          <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10" />
            <path d="M12 16v-4M12 8h.01" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h4 class="font-bold text-white mb-2">Precision</h4>
        <p class="text-sm text-zinc-400 leading-relaxed">
          Code is law. Design is intent. Every pixel and every function must serve a purpose. Randomness is the enemy of scale.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Value 2 -->
      <div class="p-6 rounded-2xl bg-panel border soft-border hover:border-orange-500/30 transition-colors group">
        <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-orange-500/10 flex items-center justify-center text-orange-500 mb-4 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
          <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <path d="M13 2L3 14h9l-1 8 10-12h-9l1-8z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h4 class="font-bold text-white mb-2">Velocity</h4>
        <p class="text-sm text-zinc-400 leading-relaxed">
          Speed is a feature. In the AI era, waiting is obsolete. We build systems that deploy fast and execute faster.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Value 3 -->
      <div class="p-6 rounded-2xl bg-panel border soft-border hover:border-orange-500/30 transition-colors group">
        <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-orange-500/10 flex items-center justify-center text-orange-500 mb-4 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
          <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h4 class="font-bold text-white mb-2">Autonomy</h4>
        <p class="text-sm text-zinc-400 leading-relaxed">
           Build once, run forever. We move away from manual maintenance towards self-sustaining, automated infrastructures.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>
